column5: Happy Birthday Beans!!!!!
Happy Birthday Norm. Just got this one in before it was too late (almost a belated birthday).
Happy B-day  And a dancer for you....
Happy Birthday Beans.
Happy belated birthday!!!  I hope you had a good one.
Happy Birthday you old fart and many more to come. I hope MB treats you extra special today!  All the best.  Big Cliff & Sue.
Happy Birthday Norm and all the best to you !!
Happy Birthday to you, Norm. Maribeth says you're allowed extra hugs today! Have a good one my friend.
Geez, I'm amazed you survived another year ya ol' fart .  Have a GREAT day Norm.  Maureen
have a good day Norm and go shopping for that special something....  Art
have yourself a great day
Got beaten to the 'old phart' thing,so-o-o Happy Birthday Old Pal [ya can chase me. but ya cant catch me !Lol!]
Happy Birthday Norm... Enjoy your day!  Cheers Jen
have a great day there Norm! its too bad ya cant throw a cast off your own dock on your bday
Happy Birthday.
Happy to ya Norm,hope you have a peaceful day. Joe
Happy Birthday Beans. Hope you have a great day.
HAPPY BIRHTDAY TO YOU!!!!!! Hope you have a great one Norm!
Norm, excellent, another milestone conquered, good on ya, I hope you enjoy your day.
AttaBoy, Norm.  For those that haven't met Norm, he is the embodiment of our little community here.  Happy Birthday and Best Fishes, Beans.
enjoyed fishing with you at Tylers event.  Happy Birthday!  TB
Thanks All...much appreciated...  Hey Wayne...I just realized, you are two days older than me  ...  Happy Belated Birthday !!!
Hey Norm have a great one!!!!!  Looking forward to seeing you this June!
I feel like it this morning as well Norm!  Hope you have a great day Norm and many more in the years to come.
Happy birthday ya cool cat you.  Enjoy yer day and heres to many more.
Happy Birthday Norm.  Hope Maribeth is treating you extra special today.  Joey
HAPPY BIRTHDAY Norm ... Hope you have a great day

Man...... Seems like a baby boom happened.. QUITE A FEW YEARS AGO I MIGHT ADD!!! LOL.... all these birthdays bunched up together... I missed this post...  Beans Happy Birthday Brother... I hoped you enjoyed your day!  Gerritt.
Happy Birthday Bean's...  Hope it was a good one...
Happy Birthday Norm,hope you had a great day.  Norm,just make sure you put a helmet on when you go ATV,with Big Cliff.  Steve
